data.value:
• Membership : Establish clear guidelines for membership, including eligibility requirements, membership fees, and the process for becoming a member.
• Code of Conduct : Set expectations for behavior and conduct of members, including respect for other members, adherence to club rules, and professionalism.
• Meetings : Establish guidelines for meetings, including frequency, duration, and agenda. Consider using a meeting management tool to help organize meetings, set agendas.
• Communication : Establish clear lines of communication between members, including email lists, forums, and social media groups.
• Events : Plan and organize events, including meetings, social events, and community service activities. Establish guidelines for event planning and management.
